data.text:
Hortense de Beauharnais and Louis Bonaparte were married for 35 years before Hortense de Beauharnais died, leaving behind her partner and 3 children.

They had 3 children, Napoléon Louis Charles (221), Napoléon Louis (219) and Charles Louis Napoléon (216).
